snippet.title: Dread Delusion - First Trailer
snippet.description:
At the edge of the world lies the citadel of the Clockwork God, where state-approved magic is regulated by strange machines. 



Dread Delusion is an upcoming low-poly open-world RPG.


Grab the early access alpha on Patreon:
https://www.patreon.com/LovelyHellplace



Or find out more details on the Itch page:
https://lovelyhellplace.itch.io/dread-delusion
